commit.message:
Makefile.in (typeck2.o): Depend on output.h.

	* Makefile.in (typeck2.o): Depend on output.h.
	* typeck2.c: Include output.h.

From-SVN: r30411

+	(no_linkage_helper): Likewise.
+	(copy_tree_r): New function.
